contents:
The Socool Team was founded on the simple idea of being able to get users to get value anytime, anywhere.
One day when I was browsing the Internet, I was suddenly awakened by an idea, that is, there is too much information on the Internet! This means that there are too many things that can be of value to us. But how do we get them?
Search engines, forums, random discovery, online sharing, group chat…
However, the excessive amount of information is a kind of consumption for me, because I spend too much time on other interference information in order to find information that I am satisfied with!
So we decided to open up a new way for users to get value: carefully selected by us, based on the quality of the resources, timeliness, difficulty of access, scarcity, pick out the most worthwhile information in the moment, and share our most Resources that you want users to know and get!
In this way, a large amount of time for searching and eliminating unwanted interference is shortened.
Moreover, the user can obtain such value inadvertently or anytime, anywhere, because our push is uninterrupted and stable. Users don’t need to care about when they should know what’s going on. This problem is completely solved by us! So, Socool Team is your ultimate resource collection.
